  "intent": "Execute a magnetic bead-based nucleic acid purification protocol using a 96-well deep-well plate on a magnetic module. Transfer lysis buffer between designated columns (A4\u2192A3, A10\u2192A9) with 150\u00b5L volumes and 20-cycle mixing at 150\u00b5L. Combine lysates with magnetic beads in columns A1 and A7 using 200\u00b5L transfers, add isopropanol for precipitation, engage magnetic separation at 6mm height, remove supernatant via side aspiration to avoid bead pellet disruption. Perform two sequential wash cycles with 150\u00b5L volumes, engage magnetic separation between steps, and conclude with 50\u00b5L elution buffer addition, final magnetic separation, and 40\u00b5L purified nucleic acid transfer to PCR aluminum block.",
